NAME
    Games::PuzzleCars - Puzzle game involving cars

SYNOPSIS
        perl puzzlecars.pl

    Options:
        --easy    Use the easy map
        --hard    Use the hard map

INSTRUCTIONS
    Click on the intersections to change which way the cars will turn.  Try to
    match the cars' color with the road they use to exit the screen to earn
    points.  If the colors don't match, you lose points.

PREREQUISIES
    * SDL
    * Mouse
